                </a>
                <div class="answer">
                    <p>
                        C++ supports the object-oriented programming, the four major pillar of object-oriented programming (OOPs) used in C++ are:<br>
                        1. Inheritance<br>
                        2. Polymorphism <br>
                        3. Encapsulation<br>
                        4. Abstraction
                    </p>
